      "title": null,
      "content": "谷歌看起来要发布 Veo 4 了，也有可能是其他的名字。 类似 Seedance 2.0 的全能参考，支持对视频进行：修改参考和内容替换 质量上看起来，在文字生成上要比 Seedance 2.0 稍微好点，但在其他方面看不出更好的质量，可能在清晰度和细节上也会稍微好点。 Video 🚨 AI News | TestingCatalog (@testingcatalog) GOOGLE 🔥: An upcoming Gemini Omni video model from Google is expected to be much more advanced in video editing, capable of completing tasks like removing watermarks, replacing objects in the video, and more. It is also likely that Google will release 2 versions of this model, including a Pro variant. And I assume what we see isn't Pro? Anime sample 👀 Video — https://nitter.net/testingcatalog/status/2053857806374064496#m",
